cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "IMOMD-RRTStar-rs: A Rust Reproduction of Informable Multi-Objective and Multi-Directional RRT*"
message: "If you use this software, please cite both the original research paper and this software repository."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Euraxluo
    email: euraxluo@outlook.com
repository-code: "https://github.com/Euraxluo/IMOMD-RRTStar-rs"
url: "https://github.com/Euraxluo/IMOMD-RRTStar-rs"
abstract: >-
  Open-source Rust reimplementation of Informable Multi-Objective and
  Multi-Directional RRT* (IMOMD-RRT*), with a pause/resume anytime API,
  Python bindings, OSM loaders, a pluggable realtime navigation session,
  and a FastAPI V2X demonstration. Intended for algorithmic reproduction,
  teaching, and experimental comparison against the original C++ reference.
keywords:
  - motion planning
  - RRT*
  - multi-objective path planning
  - anytime algorithms
  - Rust
  - Python
license: Apache-2.0
version: 0.1.0
date-released: "2026-07-14"
references:
  - type: article
    authors:
      - family-names: Huang
        given-names: Jiunn-Kai
